<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<title>SurgicalHub — Planning</title>
<!--[if mso]>
<style>table{border-collapse:collapse;} div,td{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;}</style>
<noscript><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml></noscript>
<![endif]-->
<style>
  @media (max-width:620px){
    .sh-container{width:100% !important;}
    .sh-pad{padding-left:20px !important;padding-right:20px !important;}
  }
</style>
</head>
{% set recipientName = surgeon.firstname ? surgeon.firstname : surgeon.email %}

<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#F5F7FA;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;">
<div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;mso-hide:all;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;color:#F5F7FA;">{{ recipientName }}, votre planning du {{ periodFrom|date('d/m/Y') }} au {{ periodTo|date('d/m/Y') }} est disponible — {{ totalCount }} missions, {{ coveredCount }} affectées.</div>
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#F5F7FA;">
<tr><td align="center" style="padding:40px 16px;">
<table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="sh-container" style="width:600px;max-width:600px;background-color:#FFFFFF;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #E7EBEF;">

<!-- Header -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:26px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #E7EBEF;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#144D38;letter-spacing:-0.2px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:3px;background-color:#42A882;margin-right:9px;"></span><span>SurgicalHub</span>
</td>
<td align="right" style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#727E8C;">Planning</td>
</tr></table>
</td></tr>

<!-- Title -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:28px 32px 6px 32px;">
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:23px;font-weight:800;color:#16202B;line-height:1.3;">Votre planning est disponible</div>
</td></tr>
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:0 32px 20px 32px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#EDF4FF;color:#1B5FD0;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;padding:6px 13px;border-radius:100px;">{{ periodFrom|date('d/m/Y') }} → {{ periodTo|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
</td></tr>

<!-- Greeting -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:0 32px 22px 32px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:#3A4754;">
Bonjour {{ recipientName }},<br><br>
Veuillez trouver ci-joint votre planning pour la période du {{ periodFrom|date('d/m/Y') }} au {{ periodTo|date('d/m/Y') }}.
</td></tr>

<!-- Stats -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:0 32px 4px 32px;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td width="33%" style="background-color:#F1F4F7;border-radius:10px;padding:18px 8px;text-align:center;">
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#16202B;line-height:1.1;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;">{{ totalCount }}</div>
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#727E8C;margin-top:4px;">Missions</div>
</td>
<td width="8"></td>
<td width="33%" style="background-color:#EFFAF5;border-radius:10px;padding:18px 8px;text-align:center;">
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#144D38;line-height:1.1;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;">{{ coveredCount }}</div>
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1F6B4F;margin-top:4px;">Affectées</div>
</td>
<td width="8"></td>
<td width="33%" style="background-color:{{ uncoveredCount > 0 ? '#FEF6E7' : '#F1F4F7' }};border-radius:10px;padding:18px 8px;text-align:center;">
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:{{ uncoveredCount > 0 ? '#8A5A05' : '#98A2AE' }};line-height:1.1;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;">{{ uncoveredCount }}</div>
<div style="font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:{{ uncoveredCount > 0 ? '#B7791F' : '#98A2AE' }};margin-top:4px;">En attente d'affectation</div>
</td>
</tr></table>
</td></tr>

{% if uncoveredCount > 0 %}
<!-- Info box — same wording as before the redesign, restyled only -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:18px 32px 4px 32px;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#FEF6E7;border:1px solid #FBE8C4;border-left:4px solid #F0A91B;border-radius:10px;">
<tr><td style="padding:16px 18px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13.5px;color:#8A5A05;line-height:1.6;">
Les missions actuellement sans instrumentiste ont déjà été proposées aux instrumentistes éligibles via SurgicalHub et nous sommes en attente de leur réponse.
<br><br>
Si aucune instrumentiste n'est trouvée une semaine avant l'intervention, vous recevrez automatiquement un nouvel email afin de vous laisser le temps d'organiser, si nécessaire, une assistance opératoire avec votre firme.
</td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
{% endif %}

<!-- Attachment -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:22px 32px 4px 32px;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#F1F4F7;border-radius:10px;"><tr>
<td style="width:1%;white-space:nowrap;padding:12px 0 12px 14px;">
<span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#DDE2E8;color:#566270;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.3px;padding:5px 8px;border-radius:6px;">PDF</span>
</td>
<td style="padding:12px 14px 12px 10px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#3A4754;">Planning complet — {{ periodFrom|date('d/m') }} au {{ periodTo|date('d/m/Y') }}, en pièce jointe.</td>
</tr></table>
</td></tr>

<!-- Footer -->
<tr><td class="sh-pad" style="padding:28px 32px 30px 32px;">
<div style="border-top:1px solid #E7EBEF;padding-top:20px;font-family:Inter,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#98A2AE;line-height:1.7;">
SurgicalHub — document confidentiel, destiné uniquement à {{ recipientName }}.<br>
Cet e-mail est généré automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.
</div>
</td></tr>

</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
